        {
            "id": 6323088,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 銘旺科(2429)大跌7.28%，報65元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>銘旺科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2429:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2429\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2429-TW</a>)27日11:15股價下跌5.1元，報65.0元，跌幅7.28%，成交825張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>銘旺科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2429:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2429\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2429-TW</a>)所屬產業為光電業，主要業務為光學面板。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌5.65%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.34%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-157 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-155 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-2 張</li> <li>融資增減：-222 張</li> <li>融券增減：-17 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
